<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="nonstop-adj">nonstop <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ˌnɒn'stɒp/    美 /ˌnɒn'stɒp/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-continuous-direct">1.★ <strong>不停的；连续不断的 (continuous)；直达的 (direct)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He is on a long and nonstop journey. 
他在进行一次不间断的长途旅行。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a nonstop train 
直达列车</p></div></div>